			/>
			<h1
				class="text-black dark:text-white text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold flex flex-row gap-x-4 pb-6 lg:pb-10 text-balance"
			>
				Hey, I'm Santiago
				<a
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/santiago-franco-de-la-rosa-b657941b0/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener"
					class="flex items-center transition md:justify-center md:hover:scale-105"
				>
					<Badge>Open to work</Badge>
				</a>
			</h1>
			<h2 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl opacity-80 text-wrap max-w-[600px]">
				<span>An experienced. </span>
				<span class="text-sky-800/100 dark:text-yellow-200/90">
					Software Developer and DevOps Engineer.
				</span>
				<span class="text-orange-400 dark:text-red-200/90">
					From Colombia ðŸ‡¨ðŸ‡´.
