				</span>
			</h2>
			<nav class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-8">
				<SocialContainer
					href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/santiago-franco-de-la-rosa-b657941b0/"
				>
					<LinkedInIcon class="size-4 md:size-6" />
					LinkedIn
				</SocialContainer>
				<SocialContainer href="https://github.com/santiangofrancozx">
					<GitHubIcon class="size-4 md:size-6" />
					GitHub
				</SocialContainer>
				<SocialContainer href="mailto:santiagofrancozx@gmail.com">
					<MailIcon class="size-4 md:size-6" />
